    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@Haroenv sounds like what I'm looking for indeed.\r\nI guess a simpler configuration would've been appreciated (in the vein of the current `urlSync`), but I noticed that I'll be able to update the title as well so that sounds exactly like what I need ([by looking at this demo](http://weary-plants.surge.sh/app.js)).\r\nThis is the very last thing I need to do to fully replace our current (local) system by algolia's 🎉 \r\n\r\n_PS: unfortunately I wasn't able to play with it as this PR is based of 2.3.3 which apparently is broken with my setup._",
